    <item>
      <title>缅因州的一个部落正在汗水小屋中使用阿片类药物解决资金来治疗毒瘾</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/12/1250379089/sweat-lodge-traditional-healing-addiction-recovery-opioid-settlement-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数百个美洲原住民部落正在从与阿片类药物公司的诉讼和解中获得资金。一些人将新资金投资于传统治疗方法以治疗毒瘾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/05/12/1250379089/sweat-lodge-traditional-healing-addiction-recovery-opioid-settlement-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 11:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
