    <item>
      <title>阿富汗山洪已造成300多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/11/1250767210/afghanistan-flash-flood-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国粮食机构称，季节性大雨造成的洪水已摧毁了 1000 多所房屋。一名联合国官员表示，洪水提醒人们阿富汗在气候危机面前的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/11/1250767210/afghanistan-flash-flood-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 13:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
